{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I used to take off my-- everybody had to carry-- I mean, to wear sewed in Jewish stars from the front and from the back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had to be sewed in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They couldn't be just stapled in or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to take them off from time to time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to go out and communicate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a good relationship with certain people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to help some of my friends who went to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was pretty aware of what's happening, what's going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My uncle was-- and I listened to him because he was a leader in the community at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he just didn't want me to go to the partisans because many of my friends, some of my friends were killed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was extremely dangerous, and he felt that him and my grandmother, who, I was like the idol for her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I tried to work from inside and tried to be helpful in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it came already to a point where I saw that the ghetto is being liquidated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although many people felt, especially with what's happening on the front, with the German defeat, and all the political atmosphere have changed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw also that-- and we became-- in 1943, we became a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because, before that, we used to be watched by Wehrmacht, by the-- by the-- just by the military.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now we were assigned to the SS, and they were terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to have Hungarian SS people who were terrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were even worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We used to have SS people from the Russians, from Ukrainians, from the Vlasov's army who were Russians, who helped the German, and who were aligned and affiliated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
